  "title": "Context-Insensitive vs 1-CFA Pointer Analysis",
  "example": {
    "code": "int *identity(int *x) { return x; }\nint main() {\n    int a, b;\n    int *p = identity(&a);\n    int *q = identity(&b);\n}",
    "language": "c"
